<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
	<meta charset="gbk" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"  />
	<title>POCO授权</title>
	<style type="text/css">
		body,div,dl,dt,dd,ul,ol,li,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6,pre,code,form,fieldset,legend,input,textarea,p,blockquote,th,td{margin:0;padding:0}
		article,aside,details,figcaption,figure,footer,header,hgroup,menu,nav,section{display:block}
		fieldset,img{border:0}
		table{border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0}
		li{list-style:none}
		a,a:hover{text-decoration:none;color:#ffe400;}
		a, textarea, input, button { outline: none }
		* { -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-appearance: none; }
		html { 
			-ms-touch-action: none;
			font-size: 62.5%;
		}
		body{
			background: #fff;
			-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);
		}
		html, body { 
			font-family:"Microsoft Yahei",Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif,Arial;
		}
		input,select,button{
		    -webkit-appearance:none;
		    appearance:none; 
		    border-radius: 0; 
		}
		input[type="submit"],input[type="reset"],input[type="button"],input{-webkit-appearance:none;}

		.authorize-page .bar-item{
			background: #222;
			text-align: center;
			color: #fff;
			padding: 2.365% 0;
		}
		.authorize-page .bar-item h2.title{
			font-weight: normal;
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}

		.authorize-page .content{
			padding: 20.5% 5% 0;
		}
		.authorize-page .info-item{
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			text-align: center;
			color: #666;
			padding-bottom: 20.5%;
			line-height: 1.5;
		}
		.authorize-page .btn-wrap .btn-item{
			display: block;
			width: 100%;
			font-size: 1.4rem;
			color: #fff;
			text-align: center;
			padding: 2% 0;
			background: #444;
			margin-bottom: 2.78%;
			border-radius: 5px;
		}
		.authorize-page .btn-wrap .btn-Refuse{
			background: #aaa;
		}
		
		@media screen and (max-width: 768px) and (max-height: 1024px) {
			html { 
					font-size: 133.33%; 
			} 
		}
		@media screen and (max-width: 621px) and (max-height: 1044px) {
			html { 
					font-size: 107.8125%; 
			}
		}
		@media screen and (max-width: 540px) and (max-height: 960px) {
			html { 
					font-size: 93.75%; 
			} 
		}
		@media screen and (max-width: 414px) and (max-height: 736px) {
			html { 
					font-size: 71.875%; 
			} 
		}
		@media screen and (max-width: 375px) and (max-height: 627px) {
			html { 
					font-size: 65%; 
			} 
		}
		@media screen and (max-width: 360px) and (max-height: 640px) {
			html { 
					font-size: 62.5%; 
			} 
		}
		@media screen and (max-width: 320px) and (max-height: 568px) {
			html { 
					font-size: 55.56%; 
			} 
		}
	</style>

<body>
	<section class="authorize-page">
		<hgroup class="bar-item">
			<h2 class="title">POCO授权</h2>
		</hgroup>
		<div class="content">
			<article class="info-item">
				<p>
					授权后将允许“三星 盖乐世社区”链接你的POCO账号同步网站个人资料，请信任“三星 盖乐世社区”再点击“授权”按钮，不会获得你的POCO账号/密码。
				</p>
			</article>
			<section class="btn-wrap">
				<a href="#" class="btn-item btn-authorize">授权</a>
				<a href="#" class="btn-item btn-Refuse">拒绝</a>
			</section>
		</div>
	</section>
</body>
</html>